              <tr><td>Cheapest model</td><td>¥0.006/1K (Lite)</td><td>~$0.001/1K (V3)</td><td>¥0.01/1K</td></tr>
              <tr><td>WeChat integration</td><td>✅ Native</td><td>❌ None</td><td>❌ None</td></tr>
              <tr><td>China speed</td><td>Extremely fast</td><td>Fast</td><td>Fast</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Free tier</td><td>Limited free calls</td><td>¥10 free credits</td><td>First ¥10 free</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Context window</td><td>128K</td><td>128K (DeepSeek-V3)</td><td>128K</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How to Get Started with Hunyuan API</h2>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Create a Tencent Cloud account</strong> — Sign up at <a href="https://cloud.tencent.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cloud.tencent.com</a> if you don't already have one</li>
          <li><strong>Enable Hunyuan service</strong> — Navigate to Tencent Cloud's AI services console and activate Hunyuan API</li>
          <li><strong>Generate an API key</strong> — Create your secret credentials for authenticating API requests</li>
          <li><strong>Choose your model tier</strong> — Start with Hunyuan-Lite for cost testing, then upgrade based on your quality needs</li>
          <li><strong>Integrate into your application</strong> — Use Tencent Cloud's SDK or direct API calls; for WeChat mini programs, leverage the built-in integration</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq">
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Q: Is Tencent Cloud Hunyuan API free to use?</strong></summary>
            <p>A: Yes, Hunyuan offers a free tier with monthly API call quotas. Beyond the free allocation, pricing starts at ¥0.006/1K input tokens for Hunyuan-Lite, making it one of the most affordable domestic AI APIs in China.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Q: How does Hunyuan compare to DeepSeek on pricing?</strong></summary>
            <p>A: Hunyuan-Lite (¥0.006/1K input) is slightly more expensive than DeepSeek-V3 (~$0.001/1K input) but offers free tier access. Hunyuan-Pro (¥0.12/1K input) is comparable to GPT-4o mini ($0.15/1M input) when converted to USD.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Q: Can I use Hunyuan API with WeChat mini programs?</strong></summary>
            <p>A: Yes, one of Hunyuan's standout features is its deep integration with Tencent's ecosystem — WeChat, QQ, WeChat Work, and Tencent Cloud services. This makes it ideal for building AI-powered mini programs and enterprise WeChat applications.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Q: What models are available in Hunyuan API?</strong></summary>
            <p>A: Hunyuan-Pro is the flagship model for complex reasoning and tasks; Hunyuan-Standard balances performance and cost; Hunyuan-Lite is the budget option; and Hunyuan-Function supports function calling for AI agent workflows.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary><strong>Q: Does Hunyuan API work well in mainland China?</strong></summary>
            <p>A: Hunyuan API is hosted on Tencent Cloud infrastructure in mainland China, providing extremely fast response times and reliable access for China-based applications. No VPN or proxy required.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>Tencent Cloud Hunyuan API is the natural choice for developers already invested in the Tencent ecosystem — particularly those building WeChat mini programs, WeChat Work applications, or services running on Tencent Cloud. Its native integration advantages are unmatched by any competitor, and the Hunyuan-Lite tier offers genuinely competitive pricing for high-volume simple tasks.</p>
        <p>For pure model capability and benchmark performance, Hunyuan trails behind DeepSeek-V3 and GPT-4o. But for China-based applications where speed, reliability, and ecosystem fit matter more than raw benchmark numbers, Hunyuan is a compelling option. Start with the free tier to validate it works for your specific use case.</p>
        <p><strong>Ready to get started?</strong> Visit <a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/document/product" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tencent Cloud AI Services</a> to enable Hunyuan API and create your first API key today.</p>
        <p><em>Compare Hunyuan with other providers on <a href="/providers/tencent/">APIRank</a> — real-time pricing, availability in China, and provider reviews.</em></p>
      </section>
    </div>

